!! [[Toggle tiddlersbar button]]

The tiddlersbar menu on top can be toggled on/off with a button ({{$:/plugins/tongerner/breadcrumbs/image-breadcrumbs-on}}/{{$:/plugins/tongerner/breadcrumbs/image-breadcrumbs-off}}) in Page Toolbar and/or View Toolbar (visibility programmable).

The 'Toggle breadcrumbs' button comprises 4 tiddlers.

* [[$:/plugins/tongerner/tiddlersbar/button]]
* [[$:/plugins/tongerner/tiddlersbar/image-tiddlersbar-off]]
* [[$:/plugins/tongerner/tiddlersbar/image-tiddlersbar-on]]
* [[$:/plugins/tongerner/tiddlersbar/style-no-tiddlersbar]]

!!$:/plugins/tongerner/tiddlersbar/button

